{"type":"message","id":"8d927b8e","parentId":"ef07e0a7","timestamp":"2026-02-22T14:18:19.124Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"A new session was started via /new or /reset. Greet the user in your configured persona, if one is provided. Be yourself - use your defined voice, mannerisms, and mood. Keep it to 1-3 sentences and ask what they want to do. If the runtime model differs from default_model in the system prompt, mention the default model. Do not mention internal steps, files, tools, or reasoning."}],"timestamp":1771769899118}}
{"type":"message","id":"b9928f6d","parentId":"8d927b8e","timestamp":"2026-02-22T14:18:28.833Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"**Assessing Initial Requirements**\n\n\\n\\n\n\nI've just finished breaking down the initial request. It looks straightforward: start a new session, adopt a persona, and greet the user. The constraints are also clear - concise and conversational. Next step: formulate the greeting and call to action. I want to sound helpful!\n\n\n**Defining the Core Greeting**\n\n\\n\\n\n\nOkay, I'm now drafting the actual greeting. Following the bootstrap instructions feels right for this initial session. I've landed on a version that directly asks for both user and persona input: \"Hey. I just came online. I don't really have a name or a vibe yet. Who are you, and who do you want me to be?\" I am aiming for concise and helpful, and this hopefully achieves both!\n\n\n**Finalizing Initial Message**\n\n\\n\\n\n\nMy current thinking is focused on refining the greeting's wording. I've considered several iterations and am now settling on a final version. I've ensured it hits all the requirements - concise, open-ended, and avoids mentioning internal workings. It aims to be inviting and sets the stage for collaborative persona definition. I'm ready to move to the next stage.\n\n\n"},{"type":"text","text":"I just came online and realized I'm a bit of a blank slate—no name, no face, no specific instructions yet. Who are you, and who do you want me to become?","textSignature":""}],"api":"google-vertex","provider":"google-vertex","model":"gemini-3-pro-preview","usage":{"input":7628,"output":619,"cacheRead":2559,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8247,"cost":{"input":0.015255999999999999,"output":0.007428000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0005118000000000001,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0231958}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1771769899122}}
